data.description: This charming tri-level brick home is located on an almost quarter acre corner lot across from a large public park and is surrounded by mature trees. The main level of the home boasts newly refinished hardwood floors through the spacious living and dining room leading into the tastefully remodeled kitchen and home office suite. As you walk upstairs you are greeted by a bathroom, two bedrooms and plenty of storage in the built in hallway closets. On the lower level you will find another bathroom, your garage access, huge laundry/mudroom and backyard access. The fully finished basement has a large great room with a brick fireplace and 3rd bedroom. Outside you will find a covered back porch, brick firepit and 3/4 of the lot with privacy fencing. Hail resistant roof put on in 2021. This home has it all!!
